with data as (
SELECT "cube_financial"."company" AS "company", "cube_financial"."date" AS "date", sum("cube_financial"."amount")*-1 AS "sum"
FROM "cube_financial"
WHERE "cube_financial"."account" = 'Bank' AND {{classroom}} AND {{game}}
GROUP BY "cube_financial"."company", "cube_financial"."date"
ORDER BY "cube_financial"."company" ASC, "cube_financial"."date" ASC
)
SELECT company, date, sum(sum) over (partition by company order by date asc rows between unbounded preceding and current row) FROM data

SELECT 
  "sales"."date" AS "date",
  "sales"."company" AS "company", 
  (
    (
      CAST(
        (
          sum("sales"."sum") - sum("inventory"."COGS")
        ) AS float
      ) / CASE WHEN sum("sales"."sum") = 0 THEN NULL ELSE sum("sales"."sum") END
    ) * 100
  ) AS "Gross margin" 
FROM 
  (
    SELECT 
      "cube_sales"."company" AS "company", 
      "cube_sales"."classroom" AS "classroom", 
      "cube_sales"."game" AS "game", 
      "cube_sales"."date_invoice" AS "date",
      sum("cube_sales"."price_total") AS "sum" 
    FROM 
      "cube_sales" 
    WHERE 
  (
    {{ classroom }} AND
    {{ game }}
  ) 
    GROUP BY 
      "cube_sales"."company", 
      "cube_sales"."classroom", 
      "cube_sales"."game", 
      "cube_sales"."date_invoice"
  ) "sales" 
  INNER JOIN (
    SELECT 
      "cube_inventory"."company" AS "company", 
      "cube_inventory"."game" AS "game", 
      "cube_inventory"."classroom" AS "classroom", 
      "cube_inventory"."date",
      (
        sum("cube_inventory"."valuation") * -1
      ) AS "COGS" 
    FROM 
      "cube_inventory" 
    WHERE 
      "cube_inventory"."destination" = 'Customers' 
    GROUP BY 
      "cube_inventory"."company", 
      "cube_inventory"."game", 
      "cube_inventory"."classroom",
      "cube_inventory"."date"
  ) "inventory" ON (
    "sales"."company" = "inventory"."company" 
    AND "sales"."classroom" = "inventory"."classroom" 
    AND "sales"."game" = "inventory"."game" 
    AND "sales"."date" = "inventory"."date"
  ) 
GROUP BY 
  "sales"."company", 
  "sales"."date"
ORDER BY 
  "sales"."date" ASC, 
  "sales"."company" ASC
